Class AbstractCasWebflowConfigurer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.web.flow.AbstractCasWebflowConfigurer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    @Component(value="casWebflowConfigurer")
public abstract class AbstractCasWebflowConfigurer
extends java.lang.Object
    The AbstractCasWebflowConfigurer is responsible for providing an entry point into the CAS webflow.
